      <title><![CDATA[Material主题的改造]]></title>
      <url>https://stevenxiaoming.github.io/2017/03/23/Material%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E6%94%B9%E9%80%A0/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>我的博客就是基于hexo-theme-material主题进行改造的，我不是前端攻城狮，所以写的烂，仅供参考，请勿吐槽……</p>
<p><a href="https://github.com/viosey/hexo-theme-material" target="_blank" rel="external">material主题源码</a></p>
<p>目前还没找到代码染色，等找到代码染色后更新一下，看得更舒服更清楚一点 Orz</p>
<h2 id="首页文章添加标签"><a href="#首页文章添加标签" class="headerlink" title="首页文章添加标签"></a>首页文章添加标签</h2><ul>
<li>在主题文件夹 layout_partial 内找到 Paradox-post_entry.ejs 文件</li>
<li>找到<figure class="highlight erb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- Category --&gt;</span></span></div><div class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"post_entry-category"</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">%-</span></span><span class="ruby"> list_categories(post.categories, &#123;</span></div><div class="line">            <span class="symbol">show_count:</span> <span class="literal">false</span>,</div><div class="line">            <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span>: '<span class="title">post_tag</span>',</span></div><div class="line">            <span class="symbol">style:</span> <span class="string">'none'</span></div><div class="line">        &#125;) <span class="xml"><span class="tag">%&gt;</span></span></div><div class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<p>这是显示分类的代码</p>
<ul>
<li>在这段代码前添加<figure class="highlight erb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- Tags --&gt;</span></span></div><div class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"post_entry-category"</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">%-</span></span><span class="ruby"> list_tags(post.tags, &#123;</span></div><div class="line">            <span class="symbol">show_count:</span> <span class="literal">false</span>,</div><div class="line">            <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span>: '<span class="title">post_category</span>',</span></div><div class="line">            <span class="symbol">style:</span> <span class="string">'none'</span></div><div class="line">        &#125;) <span class="xml"><span class="tag">%&gt;</span></span></div><div class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span>&amp;nbsp;|<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<p>这一段就是添加标签的代码，第10行是“|”分割符，用于分割标签和分类</p>
]]></content>
      
